headline.print_headline: Sandwich Chain Quiznos Files for Bankruptcy Protection
headline.main: Sandwich Chain Quiznos Files for Bankruptcy Protection

lead_paragraph: Sandwich chain Quiznos Corp filed for pre-packaged bankruptcy protection on Friday after struggling for years with high debt and rising competition.
